rows.label: qst001701_msg001
rows.name: Bring it quickly.

rows.label: qst001701_msg002
rows.name: Thank you very much.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, you brought it. I've
been waiting for you...

rows.label: qst001602_msg0002
rows.name:
Now, let's try out the
new menu right away.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd like you to taste-test it,
so please wait just a moment.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0004
rows.name: This is New Dish Name (temp)!

rows.label: qst001602_msg0005
rows.name: Go on, have a taste!

rows.label: qst001602_msg0006
rows.name:
See, it's delicious, right?
It's a high-class dish that
costs 5000G per plate!

rows.label: qst001602_msg0007
rows.name:
You have to defeat Enemy Name
1 (temp) and Enemy Name 2 (temp),
so it's quite expensive.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0008
rows.name:
...But no one around here would
eat such an expensive dish!!

rows.label: qst001602_msg0009
rows.name:
Of course not. Do you think
rich people live around here?

rows.label: qst001602_msg0010
rows.name:
The people who live around here are
the ones who work at the hot springs
or the giant heat extraction ducts.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0011
rows.name:
They wouldn't pay 5000G for a single
dish. I need to come up with a dish
that's more popular with them.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0012
rows.name: I can't believe I overlooked that...

rows.label: qst001602_msg0013
rows.name:
Sorry, but could you
do me one more favor?

rows.label: qst001602_msg0014
rows.name:
I need you to get me some Puri Leaf
Cabbage and Crunchy Passion Fruit.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0015
rows.name:
The taste might be a bit worse,
but I think I can make something
cheap and delicious with these.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0016
rows.name:
For the Puri Leaf Cabbage, the
ones from Avaritia are best.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0017
rows.name:
You should be able to find Crunchy
Passion Fruit in Superbia.

rows.label: qst001602_msg0101
rows.name:
With these two, I can
complete the new menu!
